-- Better Place’s Ofer Sees 2015 as Tipping Point for Electric Cars
-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 2012-01-27T06:50:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/better-place-s-ofer-sees-2015-as-tipping-point-for-electric-cars.html
Better Place LLC, a U.S. startup
developing charging stations for electric vehicles, expects the
“tipping point” for its business to come as soon as 2015,
Chairman Idan Ofer said at the  World Economic Forum  in Davos.
Switzerland today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
